{"tid":1965633,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武肺真手足】染疫46歲PTU男沙展肺衰竭入ICU插喉 曾驅散悼8.31群眾","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T15:09:10.000Z","uid":113368,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4368d2a182d294d30c22e222b2a2d00fc26dcf","tid":1965633,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"本港3萬名警察，至今已有4位確診武漢肺炎。上月31日曾在港鐵太子站外驅散悼念8.31群眾的46歲PTU男沙展，是第4位染疫的香港警察，成為本港第854號患者，留醫伊利沙伯醫院。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>據悉，該男警病情轉差，有肺衰竭，今日（9日）要入住深切治療部插喉。</strong></span></span></span>他在病毒潛伏期間，曾與第3名確診的警察（第663號患者，入院時肺部已纖維化）共用石硤尾警署同一樓層的洗手間。122名曾使用有關設施的警察，要入隔離營檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200409&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60811797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200409%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60811797&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=73f7b1a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200409%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60811797&h=e97b9f10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200409&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60811797</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我好撚興奮呀！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uMGcAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uMGcAm.jpg&h=a97717cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"103b381665d10dd73c16c75f9898d2deffcca8b7","tid":1965633,"uid":113368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rc5LEfR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frc5LEfR.jpg&h=fdb77fed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54f2f4e204438a44f2221852c3dcb67be20c748e","tid":1965633,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,